            <a href="#contact" class="text-xs font-mono text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/30 px-3 py-1.5 rounded bg-emerald-500/5 hover:bg-emerald-500/10 transition-colors">
                &gt; connect_
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-24 space-y-32">

        <!-- 1. Hero Section -->
        <section id="hero" class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center">
            
            <!-- 3D Terminal Window -->
            <div class="w-full max-w-3xl animate-float cyber-glow bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative">
                <!-- Terminal Header -->
                <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border-b border-zinc-800 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
                    <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50"></div>
                    <div class="mx-auto text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500">root@ab-system:~</div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Terminal Body -->
                <div class="p-8 md:p-12 text-left relative">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-emerald-500/20 to-transparent"></div>
                    
                    <p class="font-mono text-emerald-500 mb-4 text-sm md:text-base flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="text-zinc-500">$</span> ./init_profile.sh
                    </p>
                    
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-medium text-zinc-100 tracking-tight mb-4 inline-block typing-effect">
                        Aryan Bhattarai
                    </h1>
                    
                    <div class="font-mono text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-400 mb-8 space-y-2">
                        <p>&gt; <span class="text-emerald-400">Cybersecurity Enthusiast</span></p>
                        <p>&gt; <span class="text-emerald-400">Web Developer</span></p>
                        <p>&gt; <span class="text-emerald-400">Ethical Hacking Learner</span></p>
                    </div>

                    <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-emerald-500/30 pl-4 py-1 mb-8 text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-400 italic">
                        “Started with curiosity about how the internet works. Now I build secure websites and study cybersecurity to protect systems from attacks.”
                    </blockquote>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm font-mono text-zinc-500 mb-10">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:map-point-linear" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
                            Kathmandu, Nepal
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <iconify-icon icon="solar:laptop-minimalistic-linear" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
                            Cybersecurity &amp; Web Dev
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                        <a href="#projects" class="bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/50 hover:bg-emerald-500 hover:text-zinc-950 px-6 py-2.5 rounded font-mono text-sm transition-all duration-300">
                            View Projects
                        </a>
                        <a href="#contact" class="bg-transparent text-zinc-300 border border-zinc-700 hover:border-zinc-500 px-6 py-2.5 rounded font-mono text-sm transition-all duration-300">
                            Contact Me
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. About Me -->
        <section id="about" class="scroll-mt-32">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-100 tracking-tight font-mono">01. About_Me</h2>
                <div class="h-px bg-zinc-800 flex-1"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-6 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        Hello, I'm <span class="text-emerald-400 font-mono">Aryan Bhattarai</span>, a cybersecurity enthusiast and web developer from Nepal.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        My journey into technology started with curiosity about how websites work and how hackers exploit vulnerabilities. Instead of using that knowledge for harm, I focused on learning ethical hacking, security testing, and web development.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Over time, I built projects, practiced penetration testing in lab environments, and improved my skills in:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 font-mono text-xs md:text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-4">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><iconify-icon icon="solar:alt-arrow-right-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon> Web development</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><iconify-icon icon="solar:alt-arrow-right-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon> Security testing</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><iconify-icon icon="solar:alt-arrow-right-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon> Network fundamentals</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><iconify-icon icon="solar:alt-arrow-right-linear" class="text-emerald-500"></iconify-icon> Bug hunting</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="pt-4 border-t border-zinc-800/50">
                        My goal is to become a professional cybersecurity specialist who helps organizations secure their systems.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Decorative 3D Element for About -->
                <div class="relative w-full aspect-square max-w-sm mx-auto perspective-[1000px]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-emerald-500/20 to-transparent border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl transform rotate-y-[-15deg] rotate-x-[10deg] shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center p-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
                        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-emerald-500/50 opacity-70 w-full h-full overflow-hidden break-all">
